execute().details: Execute function called after deadline If threshold is met, sends all funds to ExampleExternalContract If threshold is not met, enables withdrawals

stake().details: Allows users to stake ETH before deadline Tracks individual balances and emits Stake event

timeLeft().details: Returns time remaining until deadline Returns 0 if deadline has passed

withdraw().details: Allows users to withdraw their funds if staking failed Only available if threshold was not met
